  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Tracheobronchitis as defined by:

               -  Purulent sputum with &gt; 10 x 4 CFU

               -  Leukocytosis or leukopenia

               -  Fever

               -  No pneumonia on CT scan

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Recent treatment of pneumonia

          -  Abnormal Chest X-ray

          -  Evidence of Pneumonia on CT scan
      </textblock>
